## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible solutions or perspectives on climate change. The rapidly evolving nature of climate science means that new data and technologies could alter current understandings and strategies. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude valuable insights from non-English speaking regions.